# Import Order

Group imports at the top with a blank line between groups:

1. React & Next.js (`react`, `next/link`, `next/navigation`)
2. Third-party (`axios`, `@tabler/icons-react`, etc.)
3. Path aliases (`@/api/*`, `@/ui/*`, `@/components/*`, `@/hooks/*`, `@/lib/*`, `@/types/*`)
4. Same directory (`./hooks`, `./types`)

Never use `../../` for cross-directory imports — use `@/*` aliases.
